https://hypercolor.dev/
TailwindCSS
CDN - <link href="https://unpkg.com/tailwindcss@^2/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
To Change the direction of the gradient just change the t->r or r->t [that is t-top r-right l-left and so on]

bg-gradient-to-r from-green-200 via-green-300 to-blue-500 - Seafoam
bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-300 via-purple-300 to-indigo-400 - Cotton Candy
bg-gradient-to-t from-green-200 via-green-400 to-purple-700 - Pandora
bg-gradient-to-t from-red-400 via-gray-300 to-blue-500- BombPop
